      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "INCLINATION (1) was well in the market last time but only managed eighth (31.14), beaten 12 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Should bounce back. KEY PHILOSOPHY (4) lines up here off a comfortable win at Ballarat after jumping from box 1 (25.04). Has the squeeze box to overcome and will need the breaks early. Goes well out of this box with a win and three minor placings. Should be in this for a long way. PAW RAELIA (7) has been mixing form lately, hitting the frame two back before finishing fifth (30.70) at Wentworth Park in a NG. Can turn it around this time. PAW ORENTHAL (5) is a last start winner and can go on with it.",
